[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說一切如來真實攝大乘現證",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三昧大教王經卷第二十一",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝奉大夫試光祿卿",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409a14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傳法大師賜紫沙門臣施護等奉　詔譯18 大曼拏羅廣大儀軌分大曼拏羅廣大儀軌分第十八爾時，世尊復入一切如來法三昧出生加持三摩地，說此最上自心大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　怛他引　誐多一句　葛哩摩二合引　屹哩二合　吽引二」爾時，金剛手菩薩摩訶薩說此自部羯磨出生最上自心大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409a23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　吽引　禰一句」爾時，金剛藏菩薩摩訶薩說此最上自心大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　囉怛那二合　葛哩摩二合　三摩曳引　吽引一句」爾時，金剛眼菩薩摩訶薩說此最上自心大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩彌二合引　吽引一句」爾時，金剛巧業菩薩摩訶薩說此最上自心大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　尾說葛哩彌二合引　吽引一句」爾時，聖觀自在菩薩摩訶薩說此自部羯磨曼拏羅頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409b06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今次第當演說，　　最上羯磨曼拏羅，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409b07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其相猶如金剛界，　　蓮華羯磨故此說。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409b08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依大曼拏羅法用，　　如次抨諸曼拏羅，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於佛周匝諸分位，　　畫執蓮華為標幟。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409b10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0409b11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　部引　哩尼吽引一句「唵引　尾說葛哩彌二合引　說哩吽引一句「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　怛他引　誐帶引　說哩也二合句　毘尸引　哥一句　鉢訥摩二合　尾禰曳二合引　吽引二「唵引　達哩摩二合　葛哩彌二合引　說哩一引　倪也二合引　那布引　惹引　三摩曳引　吽引二「唵引　阿謨引　伽葛哩彌二合引　說哩吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　沒提引　吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　嚩日哩二合　尼吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　哥引　彌儞一句　摩引　囉拏布引　惹引葛哩摩二合　三摩曳引　吽引二「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　覩瑟致二合　吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　勃哩二合　酤胝吽引　怛囉二合一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　蘇引　哩曳二合引　吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　特嚩二合　𡁠引　吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　賀引　西引　郝一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　多引　哩引　吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　酤摩引　哩吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　那引　囉引　野尼吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　沒囉二合引　吽彌二合引　吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　涅哩二合　怛曳二合引　說哩吽引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　葛哩摩二合　犖叉引　三摩曳引　吽引一句「唵引　摩賀引　鉢囉二合　贊尼伽引　底儞一句　鉢訥摩二合能瑟吒囉三合引　葛哩摩二合　葛哩吽引二「唵引　葛哩摩二合　母瑟致二合　伽引　怛野吽引一句「唵引　囉底布引　𡁠引　吽引　𠺁一句「唵引　阿毘尸引　哥布引　𡁠引　吽引　呼引一句「唵引　詣引　多布引　𡁠引　吽引　馱一句「唵引　涅哩二合　爹布引　𡁠引　吽引　嚩一句「唵引　度引　波布引　𡁠引　吽引　惡一句「唵引　補瑟波二合　布引　𡁠引　吽引　怛囉二合一句「唵引　阿路引　哥布引　𡁠引　吽引　提一句「唵引　巘馱布引　𡁠引　吽引　鑁一句「唵引　喝野屹哩二合引　吠引一句　阿引　那野吽引　𠺁二「唵引　阿謨引　伽播引　舍骨嚕二合引　提引一句　閉拏野吽引　發吒半音二「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　商葛羅滿提引　吽引　發吒半音一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　健吒引　吠引　舍野吽引　發吒半音一句「復次，此曼拏羅中所有鉤召等法皆依廣大儀軌作已，如其所說，引弟子入曼拏羅，謂弟子言：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善男子！",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝不應以此祕密法輒為人說，無令墮於大地獄中。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「然後為其教授智所出生懺悔智法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所有觀自在大印，　　妙等引心當觀想，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依法懺悔諸罪愆，　　速得一切罪清淨。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勝三昧耶印相合，　　觀自在尊三摩地，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切無間重罪愆，　　依法懺悔悉清淨。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀自在尊三摩地，　　妙等引心當觀想，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依法懺悔諸罪愆。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a11_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　彼一切罪皆散壞。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有羯磨印次第，　　依法若能正一結，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切業障懺悔時，　　得一切業皆清淨。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　播引　波尾輸引　達那一句　摩賀引鉢訥摩二合二「唵引　薩哩嚩二合引　難多哩也二合　尾輸引　達哥一句　摩賀引　三摩野鉢訥彌二合引二「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　播引　波鉢囉二合　那引　舍那一句　達哩摩二合　鉢訥摩二合二「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　葛哩摩二合引　嚩囉拏尾輸引　達哥一句　葛哩摩二合　鉢訥摩二合二「次當教授盡業障智法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a23_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所有觀自在大印，　　妙等引心當觀想，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "󰡊𠆙󰡊𠆙此稱時，　　一切業障皆清淨。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當結羯磨三昧印，　　觀自在尊三摩地，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沒𠆙沒𠆙此轉時，　　一切業障皆清淨。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀自在尊妙等至，　　觀想彼尊正法印，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410a28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "提提提提此說時，　　一切業障皆清淨。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次當遍結羯磨印，　　觀自在尊三摩地，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "呬呬呬呬合稱時，　　一切業障皆清淨。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　播引　波剎野鉢訥摩二合一句「唵引　阿引　嚩囉拏剎野鉢訥摩二合一句「唵引　儞引　嚩囉拏剎野鉢訥摩二合一句「唵引　葛哩摩二合　剎野鉢訥摩二合一句「次當教授一切如來供養智法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所有觀自在大印，　　妙等引心依法結，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唵唵唵唵此稱時，　　能轉一切供養事。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當結最勝三昧印，　　觀自在尊三摩地，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "部哩部哩部哩部，　　稱已得諸佛供養。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀自在尊妙等至，　　淨法蓮華當觀想，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "係係係係合稱時，　　彼得一切佛供養。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "蓮華羯磨所成印，　　住等引心依法結，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吠吠吠吠此稱時，　　彼得一切佛供養。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　唵引　哥引　囉摩賀引　鉢訥摩二合一句「唵引　部引　哥引　囉三摩野鉢訥摩二合一句「唵引　係引　哥引　囉達哩摩二合　鉢訥摩二合一句「唵引　際引　哥引　囉葛哩摩二合　鉢訥摩二合一句「次當教授成就智法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「結彼觀自在大印，　　住等引心稱紇哩，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "紇哩紇哩紇哩字，　　即得觀自在成就。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀自在尊三摩地，　　結三昧印稱室哩，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "室哩室哩室哩字，　　稱已即得勝成就。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀想觀自在等至，　　妙等引心稱狄俱，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410b28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "狄俱狄俱狄俱字，　　蓮華忿怒得成就。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼羯磨印相合故，　　大蓮華成而善妙，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉悉悉悉合稱時，　　即得一切悉地法。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　係引　悉𠆙一句「唵引　室哩二合　悉𠆙一句「唵引　狄俱半音　悉𠆙一句「唵引　悉悉𠆙一句「次當教授羯磨祕密印智法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「觀自在尊妙等至，　　一切善愛者愛樂，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿呼蘇珂此稱時，　　彼得一切佛供養。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀自在尊妙等至，　　一切善愛者喜愛，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "稱必哩曳必哩曳，　　彼得諸佛常愛樂。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c13_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀自在尊妙等至，　　一切善愛者悅樂，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿呼囉帝此稱時，　　彼常獲得妙樂事。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c15_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "觀自在尊妙等至，　　一切善愛者悅澤，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "蘇珂蘇珂此稱時，　　彼得快樂不散壞。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　布引　惹引　鉢囉二合　嚩哩多二合　那鉢訥摩二合一句「唵引　必哩二合　底葛囉鉢訥摩二合　呼引一句「唵引　囉底鉢囉二合　嚩哩多二合　那鉢訥摩二合一句「唵引　摩賀引　蘇珂鉢訥摩二合　捺哩二合　茶㰠一句「次當教授羯磨大印，如教所說當緊密合掌成三昧印，然後作金剛事業，依曼拏羅法用，於一切處以此印安布。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次當稱怛囉字，即成蓮華部羯磨法印，所有羯磨三昧法堅固作已，彼羯磨印即得成就。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0410c28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，世尊復入金剛法三昧印加持三摩地，說此自印大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　嚩日囉二合　達哩摩二合　鉢訥摩二合　吽引一句」爾時，金剛手菩薩摩訶薩說此自印大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　嚩日囉二合　劑引一句」爾時，金剛藏菩薩摩訶薩說此自印大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　嚩日囉二合　囉怛那二合　末酤胝引　吽引一句」爾時，金剛眼菩薩摩訶薩說此自印大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　達哩摩二合　鉢訥彌二合引　提引一句」爾時，金剛巧業菩薩摩訶薩說此自印大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　目契吽引一句」爾時，聖觀自在菩薩摩訶薩說此四印曼拏羅頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今次第當演說，　　最上四印曼拏羅，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其相猶如金剛界，　　大曼拏羅等無異。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四印曼拏羅中間，　　依法安布佛形像，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼尊周匝諸分位，　　當畫金剛蓮華等。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此曼拏羅中所有鉤召等法，悉依廣大儀軌作已，如其所說，引弟子入曼拏羅，謂弟子言：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『汝不應以此祕密法輒為人說，無令受於極大苦惱夭趣命終。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』「然後教授智出生法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「二手執持妙蓮華，　　一心遍取華妙香，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以此妙香普供養，　　供已速得佛成就。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a25_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶冠中有佛形像，　　妙等引心安布已，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為起世間敬愛因，　　現高舉相而順動。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "蓮華蓮華大影像，　　三摩地心所作已，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如教安坐依法儀，　　意想殺害諸魔惡。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411a29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四門遍設於蓮華，　　依法作已手中持，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "執已遍作警悟時，　　如教復作旋轉事。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　囐馱布引　惹引　屹囉二合　娑引　達野紇哩二合引一句「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　末酤吒怛他引　誐多一句　嚩尸引　酤嚕薩哩網二合引二　路引　計引　說囉那毘尸引　哥三摩野呼引三「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　鉢訥摩二合一句　摩引　囉野薩哩嚩二合鉢囉二合　爹哩體二合引　三摩引　地倪也二合引　那吠引俱半音二「唵引　尾說鉢訥摩二合一句　薩哩嚩二合　葛哩摩二合　葛嚕婆嚩二合　羅梨盧梨盧梨吽引　發吒半音三「次當教授祕密印智法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「隨彼愛樂一切事，　　此三昧能作成就，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此印能令難成法，　　於剎那間得成就。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此三昧大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　娑引　達野鉢訥摩二合一句　囉引　誐三摩野惡二「次當教結此部大印等一切印相。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，聖觀自在菩薩摩訶薩說此調伏一切世間大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　惹誐訥尾二合　那野一句　摩賀引　薩埵引　誐蹉尸引　竭囕二合二　吠引　說嚕引　必野二合　三捺哩舍二合　野三　摩摩左薩哩嚩二合　悉馱野鉢囉二合　野蹉紇哩二合四」說是大明已，即說調伏一切世間曼拏羅頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411b27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今次第當演說，　　調伏世間曼拏羅，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依大曼拏羅法用，　　外曼拏羅應遍畫。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼中宮位安蓮華，　　亦然依法周遍畫，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而諸蓮華悉開敷，　　是華復具種種色。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此曼拏羅中所有諸法用引入儀軌等，皆如廣大儀軌所說。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「次當教授調伏一切世間智法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此曼拏羅遍畫已，　　當知善調伏世間，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依法觀想大印成，　　持巧業尊等無異。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「次當教授調伏世間祕密印智法：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「所有眾色三摩地，　　妙等引心當觀想，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "蓮華金剛杵合時，　　曼拏羅法得成就。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「然後教授結彼大印等諸印相，此中所有諸成就法㡧像法等，皆依一印曼拏羅法用所作成就儀軌。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，一切如來又復雲集，咸共稱讚聖觀自在菩薩摩訶薩，頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金剛薩埵善哉者，　　金剛大寶復善哉，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善哉金剛妙法門，　　善哉金剛勝羯磨！",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能善宣說此正法，　　無上金剛祕密乘，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切如來祕密門，　　大乘現證法中攝。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」19 一切義成就大曼拏羅廣大儀軌分1一切義成就大曼拏羅廣大儀軌分第十九爾時，一切如來又復雲集，咸共稱讚已得一切如來灌頂寶者執金剛尊聖虛空藏菩薩摩訶薩，一百八名而伸勸請，頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「虛空藏尊利有情，　　摩訶薩埵大光耀，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大寶復為妙勝寶，　　稽首歸命金剛寶。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "得灌頂者大寶主，　　廣大清淨大善妙，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "覺智大寶清淨身，　　稽首歸命寶中寶。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0411c29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虛空虛空所出生，　　一切虛空大虛空，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即虛空界具諸願，　　稽首歸命諸勝願。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶中出生寶毫相，　　即佛毫相妙如來，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切上妙一切寶，　　稽首歸命寶所作。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙寶勝寶復寶勇，　　亦復為諸如來寶，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是大虛空最上寶，　　稽首歸命等虛空。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "殊妙莊嚴大嚴麗，　　眾莊嚴相妙嚴者，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "淨利清淨利有情，　　稽首歸命布施行。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "最上清淨妙法寶，　　如來復為僧伽寶，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大灌頂者利世間，　　稽首歸命第一義。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施廣施最上施，　　善捨勝捨能捨者，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "利諸有情普利已，　　稽首大利善利益。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如意寶王大威光，　　布施波羅蜜多理，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是即如來大勇猛，　　稽首歸命一切覺。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是即如來大珍寶，　　是即如來大光明，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是即如來大寶幢，　　稽首歸命大笑相。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來最上灌頂者，　　自灌頂者復大尊，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世間勝妙世間尊，　　稽首歸命世間日。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "寶中極上復極上，　　眾寶莊嚴諸寶事，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為寶世間大世間，　　稽首歸命寶名稱。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為妙寶勇復寶越，　　摩尼金剛摩尼德，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "勝妙光明寶照耀，　　稽首歸命一切寶。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大身寶杖寶自在，　　能滿一切誓願者，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已得一切意樂圓，　　稽首歸命眾寶聚。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a24_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "盡有頂際大威力，　　能施諸願大誓願，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切具足大吉祥，　　稽首歸命金剛藏。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "已受諸佛灌頂者，　　汝寂靜尊百八名，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人稱讚及受持，　　彼得剎那滅諸罪。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我今勸請汝寶主，　　善說自尊寶財藏，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛灌頂最上尊，　　真實出生祕密部。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412b01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時，聖虛空藏菩薩摩訶薩聞諸如來勸請語已，即說一切如來灌頂三昧大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412b03_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　嚩日囉二合　囉怛那二合　吽引一句」爾時，世尊大毘盧遮那如來說此摩尼寶三昧最上大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　薩哩嚩二合　怛他引　誐多引　舍引　波哩布引　囉拏一句　摩賀引　囉怛那二合　吽引二」爾時，金剛手菩薩摩訶薩說此自部出生最上大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　嚩日囉二合　囉怛那二合　吽引一句」爾時，金剛藏菩薩摩訶薩說此自部最上大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　摩尼吽引一句」爾時，金剛眼菩薩摩訶薩說此自部出生最上大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412b16_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　鉢訥摩二合　紇哩二合引一句」爾時，金剛巧業菩薩摩訶薩說此自部最上大明曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412b19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唵引　尾說囉怛那二合　吽引一句」爾時，聖虛空藏菩薩摩訶薩即入一切如來灌頂寶三摩地。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是入已，周遍從彼如來心中出現金剛摩尼寶相，廣大光明普遍照耀一切世界，以一切如來灌頂法普為一切有情作灌頂已，復聚為一體，其光旋復入具德虛空藏菩薩摩訶薩心，然後即從虛空藏菩薩摩訶薩心出現具德金剛手尊，周遍具有熾盛光藏，眾色金剛大摩尼寶、灌頂寶等妙莊嚴具莊嚴其身，執大金剛淨摩尼寶標幟印契。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出現如是大菩薩身已，廣為一切世界一切有情，雨大珍寶等，出生諸義利。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412c02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普令一切悉歡喜已，其所現身還復世尊大毘盧遮那如來周匝金剛界大曼拏羅相應月輪中，依止而住，說此頌曰：",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412c05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大哉一切正覺尊，　　一切真實珍寶藏，",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝此金剛寶部中，　　出生世間諸義利。",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412c07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說一切如來真實攝大乘現證三昧大教王經卷第二十一",
        "from": "T18n0882_021:0412c09_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]